I need to update all 8 CSS files. I'll use `sed` to do a batch replacement. The current definition is:
```css
.cn-resizable-handle-icon {
    @apply bg-border h-6 w-1 rounded-lg;
}
```

I want to change it to something that properly centers and displays the GripVertical icon:
```css
.cn-resizable-handle-icon {
    @apply flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm bg-border/70 p-0.5;
}
```

This gives the container:
- `flex items-center justify-center` - centers the icon
- `rounded-sm` - subtle rounding
